⊢ harden
  given red-team→vulnerability ≡ "Plaintext password storage and comparison..."
  given red-team→exploit ≡ "Attacker gains read access to users dict..."
  given red-team→category ≡ "auth-bypass"
  given target-code→code ≡ "def login(username, password):
